description.space:
A stay at Williamswood Castle is an epic adventure into medieval Scotland - Modeled after a Scottish hunting lodge, our guests - the lords and ladies of the estate - will enjoy such amenities as a multi-level balcony overlooking the Tennessee River, a massive bedroom complete with the Sistine Chapel painted on the ceiling, a bookshelf that moves out of the way to reveal a staircase, forty-two leaded stained glass windows, and more than 4,500 square feet of magic. 

Have a pint of ale in the Black Dog Pub, or take a walk through the more than three hundred acres of forests of Ijams Nature Center that surround the property. 

Features include the following:

-500 feet of riverfront;
-A massive multi-level deck overlooking the river;
-Ponds, and forests;
-Surrounded by 300 acres of Ijams Nature Center;
-Your very own pub;
-Three bedrooms (one of which has an antique sleigh bed that cannot accommodate anyone over six feet tall!);
-A secret passage;
-Hand-carved wood details abound;
-Dozens of pieces of antique furniture;
-The most unique and amazing house in Knoxville.

Williamswood Castle is an unforgettable adventure for the whole family!

Ideal for friend and family reunions, work retreats or a stay with friends. This splendid Victorian style residence can accommodate up to 12 people. 25 rooms including 6 bedrooms, on 4 floors with a sumptuous cachet - Beautiful solid wood doors, floors, woodwork, stained glass refurbished - High ceilings, superb fireplaces, exceptional lighting, staircase in solid wood and four fireplaces. This out of the ordinary house will offer you an unforgettable stay.

Important features:
- Possibility of swimming on the property in the Fitch river;
- Beautiful pond on the property;
- Tennis court;
- Sumptuous house, fully equipped and very comfortable;
- Functional indoor fireplace and outdoor campfire space - we provide the wood!
- Large outdoor terrace with BBQ, tables and chairs;
- Outdoor spa 4 places;
- High speed wifi connection (50 Mbit / sec);
- Game room with pool table, ping pong table and babyfoot table;
- Cellular connection is limited in the area. A landline phone will be available for you to send and receive calls.

